NOTE ON THE MUSIC FILES

The MIT licence above covers the *application code* (the HTML, CSS and
JavaScript in this repository) and the configuration files.

It does NOT cover the karaoke / MIDI files in `operas/*/` (the `.kar` files).
Those are the work of The Gilbert & Sullivan Archive (https://www.gsarchive.net)
and are included here with attribution. Please keep the credit in the page
footer, and respect the Archive's terms if you redistribute them.

The third-party sound library in `vendor/` (WebAudioFontPlayer) and the
instrument samples in `assets/instruments/` are distributed under their own
(MIT-compatible) licences by their respective authors.
